        'You are the Head of Shariah Compliance at Barakah Takaful Berhad. Upload TAK_01_Takaful_Portfolio.xlsx to Analyst and use the Surplus Distribution, Participant Fund, and Wakalah Fee Tracker tabs to test how current trends affect participant fairness, fund resilience, and the credibility of the current fee model over the next year. Quantify the downside under base, adverse, and severe scenarios and identify the indicators management should review weekly. Flag immediate pressure points as Red, elevated watch items as Amber, and stable indicators as Green. Present as a RAG table.',
