        'You are the Chief Operations Officer at Barakah Takaful Berhad. Using TAK_02_Takaful_Governance_Manual.docx and the Claim Payment Register tab in TAK_01_Takaful_Portfolio.xlsx, draft an operations memo on the most important process breakdowns, participant impacts, and control actions required before the BNM review. Show where the problems are procedural, where they are resourcing-related, and where governance escalation is needed. Present as a structured table followed by a short recommendation section.',
