        'You are the CFO of Barakah Takaful Berhad. Using the Participant Fund, Wakalah Fee Tracker, and Surplus Distribution tabs in TAK_01_Takaful_Portfolio.xlsx, create a five-slide deck on fund resilience and fee strategy. Show where pressure is concentrated, what current trends imply for surplus distribution, and what trade-offs management faces if fees are reduced or benefits are changed. Flag the priority issues on each slide as Red, Amber, or Green.',
