        'Using the Participant Fund and Surplus Distribution tabs in TAK_01_Takaful_Portfolio.xlsx, create a new worksheet called Fund and Fairness Control Tower in Excel for the web. Reorganise the information so management can see fund strain, participant impact, owner, and next intervention on one page with the most urgent items at the top. Flag severe deterioration as Red, emerging pressure as Amber, and stable areas as Green. Present as a RAG table.',
